<A>__{taylor leaps to the elevator door, but it's too late. he then sprints to the end of the hall and down the stairs.}
<B>__{taylor}
<A>__{running down the stairs and into the lobby. seeing no sign of lynn, he races out the front door to see her pulling out in a taxi. he can only stand and watch her disappear into the night.}
